for the last segment's endpoint <i>b</i>.</li>
                        <li>Evaluate the function at each applicable <i>x</=
i> value and sum the results.</li>
                        <li>Multiply the sum from step 3 with <sup>=CE=94<i=
>x</i></sup>/<sub>3</sub>.</li>
